channel.title: iPanel v3
channel.description:
Found on Rune-Serv created by Steven and Rog3r and it's not done. [b]Vid[/b]: http://tinypic.com/player.php?v=dxer9v&s=5 [img]http://moparisthebest.com/smf/Themes/default/images/bbc/quote.gif[/img]
After an absence of Steven in version two, he has came back and started working on it again. It'll have many new features and many new buttons expecting to reach double the amount of version two. Pictures speak 1000 words, just take a look at what's coming. It is expected however, that implementation may be difficult because of the abundance of features. Versions for other sources other then Devolution or Dodian derived sources be not be present. This will perhaps truly be the ultimate graphical programming interface for Devolution/Dodian.
